  <section id="architecture.connector.domain">
    <title>Connector Domains</title>
    <para>
      Although engineering systems could be a very complex system
      nevertheless all engineering teams are using the same
      tools throughout all their work. Nevertheless how complex such an
      infrastructure is you'll always find an
      <literal moreinfo="none">Issue Tracker</literal>, a
      <literal moreinfo="none">SCM</literal>
      and so on. Therefore it is possible to define base messages and base
      systems for all of them. At the moment the following types are
      designed and avaialble (or in a short period of time).
    </para>
